OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDecision due on Scotland's 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flast Covid restrictions    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Nicola Sturgeon is to confirm whether  
OL,6, Scotland's last remaining Covid        
OL,7, regulations - over the wearing of face 
OL,8, coverings - will be lifted next week.  
OL,10,FThe first minister will update MSPs on 
OL,11,Fwhether the requirement to wear masks  
OL,12,Fin shops and on public transport will  
OL,13,Fend as planned on 4 April.             
OL,15,FAll of Scotland's other Covid-19 rules 
OL,16,Fhave now been converted into guidance. 
OL,18,FBut ministers decided to keep the rule 
OL,19,Fon face coverings for an extra few     
OL,20,Fweeks due to a spike in new cases.     
